<HEADLINE>
<P>
PRAISE FOR ARTICLE ON MORMON LEADER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I appreciate the article that appeared on Howard W. Hunter, president of the 
Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints (Oct. 22).Often articles on the LDS 
Church tend to focus on issues that have little concern to the average Mormon 
and blow them all out of proportion. Often there is a critical, negative tone. 
Thank you for a straightforward, informative article. 
</P>
<P>
 STEVE GILLILAND 
</P>
<P>
 Lakewood 
</P>
