<HEADLINE>
<P>
WHY THE REFERENCES TO ROMAN CATHOLICS? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I don't know how many of my fellow communicants are behind me, but as a 
committed Catholic I was deeply disturbed by the frequent reference to the 
Roman Catholic Church in the interview with Howard Hunter.I'm tired of how 
Catholics are treated by the media. To be sure, we have our problems, but we're 
not the only church that has its shares of dissentients and sexual deviants. It 
seems that the only acceptable form of discrimination left is Catholic bashing. 
</P>
<P>
 ROSALIE MARIE WOOD 
</P>
<P>
 Torrance 
</P>
</TEXT>
