TRAIL BUILDER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I totally agree with your praise for the Mountains Conservancy Foundation's 
efforts to build and complete the Backbone Trail in the Santa Monica Mountains 
("Happy Trail," editorial, Nov. 9). 
