<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOONER OR LATER, BRUINS WILL GET IT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I noticed recently that UCLA Coach Jim Harrick has signed yet another top 
national recruit, this one from faraway Tulsa, Okla. Hmm, I wonder if (the 
player) has ever heard of Westwood and even knows that it is located out here 
in Southern California. Well, his future Bruin teammates will be able to 
straighten him out. 
</P>
<P>
 JIM SCHWEITZER 
</P>
<P>
 Brea 
</P>
