<TEXT>
<P>
 $2.3-Million Loss: Wiz Technology Inc., a San Juan Capistrano computer 
software manufacturer, recorded a loss of $2.3 million, or 36 cents a share, 
for its fiscal year ended July 31.That contrasted with profit of $75,911, or 1 
cent a share, for the previous 12 months. Revenue declined 11% to $1.7 million 
