<DOCNO> LA111994-0123 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 100097 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 19, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
