<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 19, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 5; Column 1; Metro Desk 
