<P>
61 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
SOUTHERN SECTION FOOTBALL PLAYOFF ROUNDUP; DIVISION IX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BRIAN SOBEL 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Santa Ynez 47, Calabasas 19 -- Allen Pinoli had 71 yards rushing and three 
touchdowns in 15 carries and also returned a kickoff 60 yards for a score at 
Santa Ynez (10-1). 
</P>
<P>
 Quarterback Zak Lovenson completed four of eight passes for 109 yards and one 
touchdown for Calabasas (3-8). Jeremy Marque scored on a three-yard run late in 
the fourth quarter. BRIAN SOBEL 
