Santiago; 13 at Bolsa Grande; 18 vs. Pacifica; 23 vs. Los Amigos; 25 at Rancho 
Alamitos; 27 vs. Garden Grove; 30 at Santiago. 
</P>
<P>
 February 2 vs. Bolsa Grande; 7 at Pacifica. 
